CustomField.formula:
IF( ISPICKVAL( Schedule_Frequency__c , 'D') , VALUE(Text(Frequency_Interval__c )),
IF( ISPICKVAL( Schedule_Frequency__c , 'W') ,
IF(INCLUDES( Service_Days__c , "S1"),1,0) + IF(INCLUDES( Service_Days__c , "M"),1,0) + IF(INCLUDES( Service_Days__c , "T1"),1,0) + IF(INCLUDES( Service_Days__c , "W"),1,0) + IF(INCLUDES( Service_Days__c , "T"),1,0) + IF(INCLUDES( Service_Days__c , "F"),1,0) + IF(INCLUDES( Service_Days__c , "S"),1,0),
IF( ISPICKVAL( Schedule_Frequency__c , 'M') , VALUE(Text(Frequency_Interval__c )), IF( ISPICKVAL( Schedule_Frequency__c , 'Y') , VALUE(Text(Frequency_Interval__c )), 0 ))))
CustomField.label: Final Frequency
